        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "YOU ARE HOLY, Your Name is holy,\nand those who are holy praise You every day.*\nBlessed are You, Adonai, the Holy God.\nבָּרוּךְ אַתָּה, יְיָ, הָאֵל הַקָּדוֹשׁ.\nBaruch atah, Adonai, Ha-El hakadosh.\n*SHABBAT SHUVAH -\nPraised are You, Adonai, Holy Sovereign.\nבָּרוּךְ אַתָּה, יְיָ, הַמֶּלֶךְ הַקָּדוֹשׁ.\nBaruch atah, Adonai, HaMelech hakadosh.",
          "language": "en"
        }
      ],
